nodes.text: Keenig was a Senator of the Galactic Republic who lived during the Great Galactic War with the Sith Empire. At some point between the start of the war in 3681 BBY and the Battle of Alderaan in 3667 BBY, Keenig was assassinated by Mandalorian bounty hunter Shae Vizla, which brought her to the attention of the Sith Lord Darth Malgus, and the two began a partnership as a result.

Senator Keenig is mentioned in the "Shae Vizla: Bounty Hunter" Codex entry, which is acquired during Chapter 14: Mandalore the Avenger of the 2015 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire.
